rmal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEdit: 打錯字"},{"pid":"746e090af802f29a593a78a7e14413683ffd30e0","tid":1674737,"uid":76474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3c5a6940cc200c3a3ad2f3c194588f626b53366d","tid":1674737,"uid":114875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:07:20.000Z","msg":"仲有d behavioural questions, 真係唔識簽<br />\n<br />\nBiggest failure , biggest achievement...<br />\n<br />\n小弟太廢冇achievement 更惶論要biggest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"呢d問題 係我角度黎講<br />\n係睇你個心理狀態<br />\n<br />\n答邊件事 其實唔重要<br />\n最大 呢個term人人唔同<br />\n<br />\n但答案背後呢意義 其實好影響佢對你既印象 同評價<br />\n<br />\n如果俾我 我會答得少少特別， 話即時諗到2個最大既achievement<br />\n<br />\n一個關於工作上 (保險，穩陣) <br />\n一個關於其他， 我會講釣魚 (impressive) <br />\n<br />\n你會覺得好似9 唔搭8, 但你只要hit到point就ok<br />\n<br />\n釣到大魚， 需要事前準備， 耐性， 運氣， 搏魚時收放，埋尾<br />\n<br />\n呢d正正係我平時番工做野學到同經驗<br />\n<br />\n至於 failure,  亦一樣， 佢要聽唔係係件事有幾慘 對你影響有幾大<br />\n<br />\n係你點樣面對呢個situation,  how to overcome. <br />\n<br />\nkey point我覺得係 how positive you are."},{"pid":"daadf61df38c4115e5df6e64190c0b2729e0bd0a","tid":1674737,"uid":76474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0383b698ad22824fdce9bd6255664fca594827e4","tid":1674737,"uid":250715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eeca325c7bfafc2813e301b2eebf926e0699cea4","tid":1674737,"uid":76474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76735da4691e0eac27fe9aa40351e05c9a66a498","tid":1674737,"uid":226332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾U grad，醒就唔算好醒，做野中規中矩咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過唔太識包裝自己，唔太識將缺點講到其實都唔算係缺點咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13